      "description": "# 📖 Description\n\nGear endpoints provide access to all rental equipment available on the platform.\n\nCustomers can browse equipment, view details, search, filter, and sort available gear.\n\n## 📌 Endpoints\n\n• Get All Gear  \n• Get Gear Details\n\n## 🔒 Authentication\n\nPublic\n\n## 📝 Features\n\n• Pagination  \n• Search  \n• Category Filtering  \n• Price Filtering  \n• Sorting\n\n## Query Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Description         |\n| --------- | ------------------- |\n| searchTerm    | Search by gear name, brand or description |\n| categoryId  | Filter category by id    |\n| minPrice  | Minimum price per day      |\n| maxPrice  | Maximum price per day       |\n| page      | Pagination — page number         |\n| limit     | Pagination — items per page         |\n"
    },
