                "rentals"
              ]
            },
            "description": "## Access\n\nCustomer\n\n## 📖 Description\n\nCreates a rental order and immediately initializes ###SSLCommerz payment.\n\n## 📥 Request Body\n\n``` json\n{  \n\"gearItemId\":\"uuid\",  \n\"quantity\":1,  \n\"startDate\":\"2026-07-13T00:00:00.000Z\",  \n\"endDate\":\"2026-07-16T00:00:00.000Z\"  \n}\n\n ```\n\n## 📤 Success Response\n\n``` json\n{  \n\"success\":true,  \n\"message\":\"Rental Order created successfully\",  \n\"data\":{  \n\"rentalOrder\":{\n   },\n    \"paymentUrl\":\"https://sandbox.sslcommerz.com/...\",\n    \"tranId\":\"TRNX_ID_172123123\"\n }\n}\n\n ```\n\n## 📝 Business Flow\n\nCreate Rental  \n↓  \nStock Validation  \n↓  \nRental Order Created  \n↓  \nPayment Session Created  \n↓  \nReturn paymentUrl"
          },
          "response": []
